This paprika is delicious and robust and incredibly flavorful!  It has a smoky flavor that compliments any tex-mex style cuisine.  It is fantastic sprinkled on chicken, fish, pork or tofu!!!  Add with it garlic powder, onion powder, cumin, chile and you'll have a totally authentic (uniquely/deliciously) flavored dish!  Super yummy in rice too!  Great with beans!  Basically, anywhere you'd like to try paprika that is unlike anything you'll buy in a traditional american grocery, try this!  Your family or guests will be asking you how you came up with something so delicious!  Usually only available across seas, it is a secret you will be glad you discovered!
